Quickstrike:






Quickstrike screamed in surprise at the sight of Mantella. He kicked his 
good leg up and dragged his other leg while backing into a tree behind him. 
His eyes were large and bright.

"Get away from me!" he screamed at her. "Ah'll shoot ya if ya come near me! 
Ah'll kill ya!" He raised his cobra arm up at her.
